---
title: Old Bay Breaded Shrimp and Zucchini Sticks with Roasted Sweet Potato and Lemon Chive Dipping Sauce
description: Summer may have come to an end but this shrimp dinner will have you transported back to the shoreline for the evening!  This easy Old Bay and lemon mayo breaded shrimp will have dinner on the table in no time.
